Twenty-Faux Birthday
Mark went
Labias and Gentlemen!! It’s that time of year again- where Caits is turning and unmentionable number! We can’t believe it was approximately 10 years ago that she was sneaking into bars, making out with ugly guys, and getting drunk off wine coolers. So, this year we have decided to return to her roots with a wild celebration! We’ll be heading to Old Pro for an evening of pure debauchery that will end at B412. Caitlin is going to go wild and take a shot down in only three sips!! In lieu of gifts, we ask that you make a donation to the Red Cross. SIKE! Gifts are mandatory. Preferably the kind that come in a little glass and are handed to Caitlin by a bartender. Sorry if we left you off the invite, friend lists are long, come one come all - the more the merrier.

Pre-Game Mixer Party
Mark went
*A bus will now be stopping at our place to pick us up and set us on our way to the Party* We are going to set off a pre-party soirée this Friday. We will provide all of the alcohol and you will need to bring your choice mixer to the party. That's right, vodka, gin, whiskey, tequila, and rum will all be in attendance along with their good friend "keg of beer." I repeat, this is a mixer party...WE WILL HAVE NO MIXERS, other than water, so unless you want to drink your beverages straight, please raid your local Facebook building for a nice mixer. As always, we enjoy a good party at 923 Boyce so we hope you all will have a chance to stop by and join in the celebration before the celebration.
